<div class="policy-page">
  <div class="policy-header">
    <span class="section-label">Legal</span>
    <h1 class="policy-title">Refund &amp; Return Policy</h1>
    <p class="policy-updated">Last updated: April 2026</p>
  </div>

  <div class="policy-body">

    <div class="policy-block">
      <h2>30-Day Money-Back Guarantee</h2>
      <p>We stand behind the ritual. If you do the 5-minute ritual every morning for 30 days and don't see a difference — or you simply don't love it — contact us within 30 days of delivery and we'll refund you in full. No questions asked.</p>
      <p>You don't need to return the product. Just email <a href="mailto:hello@byrituel.com">hello@byrituel.com</a> with your order number and we'll process your refund right away.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="policy-block">
      <h2>How to Request a Refund</h2>
      <p>To start a refund:</p>
      <ol>
        <li>Email us at <a href="mailto:hello@byrituel.com">hello@byrituel.com</a> within 30 days of delivery</li>
        <li>Include your order number (starts with #)</li>
        <li>Tell us briefly what wasn't right — we read every message and use it to improve</li>
      </ol>
      <p>We'll confirm your refund by email, usually within 1–2 business days.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="policy-block">
      <h2>Refund Processing</h2>
      <p>Once approved, refunds are processed to your original payment method within <strong>5–10 business days</strong>. The exact time it takes to appear on your statement depends on your bank or card issuer — sometimes it's instant, sometimes it takes a few days.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="policy-block">
      <h2>Damaged or Incorrect Items</h2>
      <p>If your order arrives damaged or you received the wrong item, contact us within <strong>7 days of delivery</strong> at <a href="mailto:hello@byrituel.com">hello@byrituel.com</a> with:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Your order number</li>
        <li>A clear photo of the damaged or incorrect item</li>
        <li>A brief description of the issue</li>
      </ul>
      <p>We'll send a replacement at no cost or issue a full refund — your choice.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="policy-block">
      <h2>Order Cancellations</h2>
      <p>If you need to cancel your order, email us as soon as possible. We try to cancel orders before they ship, but we can't guarantee cancellation once an order has been processed. If your order has already shipped, the 30-day money-back guarantee still applies.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="policy-block">
      <h2>Shipping Information</h2>
      <p>We ship throughout the United States and internationally. Standard delivery is <strong>7–14 business days</strong> after processing (2–4 business days). Tracking is provided for every order.</p>
      <p>Shipping times are estimates, not guarantees. Delays can occur due to carrier issues, customs (for international orders), weather, or other circumstances outside our control. We are not responsible for carrier-caused delays but will always help you track a package that's late.</p>
      <p><strong>Free standard shipping on orders over $35.</strong></p>
    </div>

    <div class="policy-block">
      <h2>Lost or Stolen Packages</h2>
      <p>If your tracking shows delivered but you haven't received it:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Check with neighbors and around your property</li>
        <li>Wait 48 hours (sometimes packages are marked delivered early)</li>
        <li>Contact your local carrier with the tracking number</li>
      </ul>
      <p>If the package is truly lost or stolen, email us at <a href="mailto:hello@byrituel.com">hello@byrituel.com</a> and we'll help you file a claim or send a replacement.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="policy-block">
      <h2>Contact Us</h2>
      <p>Questions about returns, refunds, or shipping? Email us anytime at <a href="mailto:hello@byrituel.com">hello@byrituel.com</a>. We typically respond within 1–2 business days.</p>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>

